title: For Sale:  For Sale: K98, 1939 J,P sauer ex sniper
postcontent: This seller is trying to sell a 147 1939 ZF41 sniper rifle without the scope. This is NOT a ZF41 rifle. Code 147 1939 JP Sauer did not manufacture ZF41 rifles. ZF41 rifles did not even come out until around 1941. His stock is also incorrect for a 1939 k98k rifle., that is the stock has a cupped butt plate instead of a flat butt plate. So the stock is not from 1939. Cupped butt plates came into use in 1940. They were phased in over time by the different factories, but by 1941 most should be cupped. The cut out on the stock for a ZF41 scope rifle was recently done and poorly done at that. Do not spend your hard earned money on this FAKE, ZF41 turd. Do a Google search on "which k98 manufacture made sniper rifles" and on a "147 1939 k98k mauser which will have a flat butt plate stock.Sellers ad here, http://www.armslist.com/posts/6548436/southeastern-pennsylvania-antiques-for-sale--k98---1939-j-p-sauer-ex-sniper
